Install Ganache -> Quickstart 
Download MetaMask Extension in Chrome
Create a new wallet
Pin the extension
Click on extension
Settings -> Network -> Add network -> Add network manually
Go to Ganache. Copy RPC Server link
Go to MetaMask. Add network. Paste RPC Server link. Chain ID: 1337. Currency symbol: ETH. Save
Click on Account. Add hardware wallet. 
Go to Ganache. Copy Address. 
Paste in details (Key & Address) 

Click on Account 2.
Send money.
